602
00:31:37,590 --> 00:31:38,440
Got it.

603
00:32:03,240 --> 00:32:06,750
Happy birthday to you!

604
00:32:11,750 --> 00:32:12,550
Thank you, everyone.

605
00:32:12,550 --> 00:32:14,110
I'm happy you're here.

606
00:32:14,790 --> 00:32:15,720
What wish did you make?

607
00:32:17,070 --> 00:32:18,240
My first wish

608
00:32:18,240 --> 00:32:22,240
