earn a lot of money,

609
00:32:22,240 --> 00:32:23,000
and be healthy.

610
00:32:23,790 --> 00:32:24,830
Yingzi, you're so greedy.

611
00:32:24,830 --> 00:32:26,030
You've already made three wishes.

612
00:32:26,480 --> 00:32:27,790
Let Yingzi continue.

613
00:32:28,160 --> 00:32:29,440
My second wish

614
00:32:29,790 --> 00:32:31,680
is that I hope you all can be with me

615
00:32:32,110 --> 00:32:33,400
on my birthday every year.

616
00:32:34,830 --> 00:32:35,510
Of course.

617
00:32:37,720 --> 00:32:38,830
My third wish is

618
00:32:40,030 --> 00:32:42,240
that there are no secrets

619
00:32:42,240 --> 00:32:43,240
between me and the person I love,

620
00:32:48,680 --> 00:32:50,070
