and honest with each other.

621
00:33:05,000 --> 00:33:05,680
Done.

622
00:33:11,270 --> 00:33:12,240
That's enough, Jiang Yi.

623
00:33:12,240 --> 00:33:13,310
Stop keeping it a secret.

624
00:33:13,310 --> 00:33:14,440
Take it out already.

625
00:33:14,440 --> 00:33:14,790
Take it out.

626
00:33:14,790 --> 00:33:15,720
Yingzi is getting anxious.

627
00:33:15,720 --> 00:33:17,030
