628
00:33:17,030 --> 00:33:18,270
A surprise.

629
00:33:21,270 --> 00:33:23,400
Take it out.

630
00:33:23,960 --> 00:33:24,590
Okay.

631
00:33:25,920 --> 00:33:26,510
Here.

632
00:33:30,510 --> 00:33:31,640
