636
00:33:49,830 --> 00:33:51,310
Yifei told you to give me this?

637
00:33:51,310 --> 00:33:52,000
Yes.

638
00:33:52,000 --> 00:33:53,750
Yifei is too busy
with her overseas tour.

639
00:33:54,160 --> 00:33:55,160
She asked for my help

640
00:33:55,160 --> 00:33:56,400
to confirm the order.

641
00:33:56,400 --> 00:33:57,680
That was why

642
00:33:57,960 --> 00:33:59,510
I logged into her email account.

643
00:34:00,070 --> 00:34:02,240
It took a long time for it
to finally reach your hands.

644
00:34:02,240 --> 00:34:03,070
Let's take a look.

645
00:34:04,310 --> 00:34:05,030
Okay.

646
00:34:10,510 --> 00:34:11,590
That's a lot.

647
00:34:11,590 --> 00:34:12,510
Look,

648
00:34:12,510 --> 00:34:14,150
overseas special edition.

649
00:34:19,920 --> 00:34:20,590
(Here you go.)

650
00:34:21,030 --> 00:34:22,030
I went to

651
00:34:22,030 --> 00:34:23,190
CD shops all over Hangtian City

652
00:34:23,190 --> 00:34:23,920
before managing to buy this.

653
00:34:25,550 --> 00:34:26,230
Yifei,

654
00:34:27,110 --> 00:34:28,030
I announce

655
00:34:28,030 --> 00:34:29,800
that besides Stefanie Sun,

656
00:34:30,230 --> 00:34:32,110
you're the woman I love the most.

657
00:34:33,230 --> 00:34:34,670
When Stefanie Sun
released albums in the past,

658
00:34:34,670 --> 00:34:36,150
