659
00:34:59,840 --> 00:35:01,670
I didn't win.

660
00:35:02,440 --> 00:35:03,280
When can I

661
00:35:03,280 --> 00:35:05,920
get to attend Stefanie Sun's concert?

662
00:35:06,230 --> 00:35:07,480
Don't be sad.

663
00:35:07,480 --> 00:35:08,920
At least we have her album.

664
00:35:10,320 --> 00:35:12,230
Yifei, I'll redeem my wish.

665
00:35:12,800 --> 00:35:13,360
What is it?

666
00:35:13,840 --> 00:35:15,510
I don't want Stefanie Sun's album.

667
00:35:15,510 --> 00:35:16,960
When we're thirty,

668
00:35:16,960 --> 00:35:19,000
let's attend
Stefanie Sun's concert together.

669
00:35:20,190 --> 00:35:20,840
Sure!

670
00:35:21,190 --> 00:35:22,550
Pinky promise.

671
00:35:29,800 --> 00:35:31,440
So? Do you like them?

672
00:35:32,070 --> 00:35:32,670
You must be elated.

673
00:35:38,630 --> 00:35:39,670
Thank you,

674
00:35:41,360 --> 00:35:42,760
but I don't think you know

675
00:35:44,400 --> 00:35:46,030
that Yifei's promise

676
00:35:47,670 --> 00:35:49,110
wasn't to give me CDs.

677
00:35:53,280 --> 00:35:54,920
This isn't from Yifei.

678
00:36:07,630 --> 00:36:08,630
How could that be?

679
00:36:23,550 --> 00:36:26,070
Urban Village, Jiangzhou Avenue.

680
00:36:27,800 --> 00:36:29,070
Urban Village.

681
00:36:33,320 --> 00:36:34,150
I'm sorry.

682
00:36:34,440 --> 00:36:34,920
I might not

683
00:36:34,920 --> 00:36:36,110
be able to stay for
today's birthday celebration.

684
00:36:36,400 --> 00:36:37,800
Ding Ye found Lan Bin.

685
00:36:37,800 --> 00:36:38,840
I need to go find him.

686
00:36:39,110 --> 00:36:39,710
Yingzi...

687
00:36:39,710 --> 00:36:39,960
Look.

688
00:36:39,960 --> 00:36:40,510
Wait.

689
00:36:40,880 --> 00:36:43,190
Chao and Yang Fan
traveled here from their hometown.

690
00:36:43,190 --> 00:36:44,760
You should at least cut the cake, right?

691
00:36:44,760 --> 00:36:45,360
Yes.

692
00:36:45,360 --> 00:36:46,030
Yang Fan also said

693
00:36:46,030 --> 00:36:47,400
she wants you to give her child a name.

694
00:36:47,400 --> 00:36:47,760
Yes.

695
00:36:47,760 --> 00:36:48,440
We were wondering

696
00:36:48,440 --> 00:36:50,230
what names you'd give to my child.

697
00:36:50,230 --> 00:36:51,510
Hurry, cut the cake.

698
00:36:51,510 --> 00:36:52,440
Cut the cake.

699
00:36:52,440 --> 00:36:52,920
Let's eat the cake first.

700
00:36:52,920 --> 00:36:53,880
Jiang Yi, don't just sit there.

701
00:36:53,880 --> 00:36:55,070
Get the stuff to cut the cake.

702
00:36:55,070 --> 00:36:56,400
Okay, that's enough!

703
00:37:00,440 --> 00:37:00,960
I...

704
00:37:01,320 --> 00:37:02,030
I really don't know

705
00:37:02,030 --> 00:37:03,590
what's wrong with you.

706
00:37:03,590 --> 00:37:05,280
Did I do anything wrong?

707
00:37:05,280 --> 00:37:06,110
You were all there

708
00:37:06,110 --> 00:37:07,190
on the day Lan Bin left, right?

709
00:37:08,190 --> 00:37:09,510
You were there

710
00:37:09,510 --> 00:37:10,510
when Yifei cried for her dad, right?

711
00:37:11,070 --> 00:37:11,840
All the while,

712
00:37:11,840 --> 00:37:13,030
Yifei wanted to find her dad.

713
00:37:13,030 --> 00:37:14,590
You know that well, right?

714
00:37:14,960 --> 00:37:16,280
Now that we've found

715
00:37:16,280 --> 00:37:17,030
Lan Bin,

716
00:37:17,030 --> 00:37:18,280
why are you stopping me?

717
00:37:18,280 --> 00:37:19,590
I really don't get it.

718
00:37:19,590 --> 00:37:20,800
Can you tell me why?

719
00:37:21,110 --> 00:37:22,360
And you, Jiang Yi.

720
00:37:22,360 --> 00:37:23,880
You've been acting strange recently.

721
00:37:24,110 --> 00:37:25,760
Can you explain about

722
00:37:25,760 --> 00:37:26,840
Yifei's email account and the CDs?

723
00:37:26,840 --> 00:37:28,230
What exactly is going on?

724
00:37:28,400 --> 00:37:30,480
Can you all explain?

725
00:37:30,880 --> 00:37:31,320
Yingzi.

726
00:37:31,320 --> 00:37:32,880
Stop! I'm not a fool!

727
00:37:32,880 --> 00:37:34,440
I know you're hiding something from me

728
00:37:34,440 --> 00:37:35,670
just like him.

729
00:37:44,150 --> 00:37:44,800
Fine.

730
00:37:46,030 --> 00:37:47,070
If you're not willing
to tell me the truth,

731
00:37:47,070 --> 00:37:48,030
never mind.

732
00:37:49,280 --> 00:37:50,480
I'll find the truth myself.

733
00:37:52,150 --> 00:37:53,480
Yingzi.

734
00:37:54,230 --> 00:37:55,230
Yingzi.

735
00:37:55,800 --> 00:37:57,070
Don't follow me!

736
00:37:58,670 --> 00:37:59,880
Especially you.

737
00:38:06,280 --> 00:38:08,190
Why is Ding Ye causing trouble now?

738
00:38:08,190 --> 00:38:09,710
We can't let Yingzi see Lan Bin.

739
00:38:10,150 --> 00:38:11,480
Both of you stay here.

740
00:38:11,840 --> 00:38:13,030
Jiang Yi and I will stop Yingzi.

741
00:38:13,030 --> 00:38:13,480
Okay.

742
00:38:13,480 --> 00:38:14,760
Yang Fan is pregnant.

743
00:38:15,150 --> 00:38:15,880
You stay with her.

744
00:38:15,880 --> 00:38:16,590
I'll head there with Jiang Yi.

745
00:38:16,590 --> 00:38:17,000
Come on.

746
00:38:17,000 --> 00:38:17,960
Enough!

747
00:38:19,590 --> 00:38:20,590
All of you stay here.

748
00:38:21,070 --> 00:38:21,960
I'll go alone.

749
00:38:23,030 --> 00:38:23,960
Wait for my news.

750
00:38:33,630 --> 00:38:34,480
Ding Ye.

751
00:38:37,840 --> 00:38:38,670
Where is he?

752
00:38:40,030 --> 00:38:41,150
Bring me to him.

753
00:38:44,550 --> 00:38:46,070
Does your friend know
you're looking for her dad?

754
00:38:47,590 --> 00:38:48,280
Yes.

755
00:38:49,030 --> 00:38:50,630
I sent her an email
to tell her about it.

756
00:38:51,030 --> 00:38:51,760
What did she say?

757
00:38:52,440 --> 00:38:54,360
She told me to stop finding him,

758
00:38:55,670 --> 00:38:56,440
but I knew deep down

759
00:38:56,440 --> 00:38:58,070
she wanted me to find her dad.

760
00:39:02,280 --> 00:39:03,400
So no matter what happens,

761
00:39:04,550 --> 00:39:05,710
you must find him?

762
00:39:06,230 --> 00:39:08,030
I must see him.

763
00:39:08,030 --> 00:39:09,630
Everything has been strange recently.

764
00:39:09,960 --> 00:39:11,510
I feel extremely confused.

765
00:39:11,510 --> 00:39:12,590
I think everyone is hiding something

766
00:39:12,590 --> 00:39:13,590
from me.

767
00:39:14,960 --> 00:39:16,400
I must see Lan Bin.

768
00:39:17,630 --> 00:39:19,110
I want to know what happened.

769
00:39:20,360 --> 00:39:21,510
All I want is an answer.

770
00:39:21,880 --> 00:39:23,590
Even if the answer is a nightmare,

771
00:39:24,670 --> 00:39:25,510
