772
00:39:34,360 --> 00:39:35,190
He's inside.

773
00:39:37,880 --> 00:39:38,590
Thank you.

774
00:40:22,880 --> 00:40:23,840
Mr. Lan.

775
00:40:31,880 --> 00:40:32,920
You are...

776
00:40:34,920 --> 00:40:35,920
Yingzi?

777
00:40:37,670 --> 00:40:38,800
