787
00:41:16,920 --> 00:41:18,880
I'd rather not know anything!

788
00:41:19,510 --> 00:41:21,150
Stop asking me!

789
00:41:32,480 --> 00:41:33,480
Mr. Lan,

790
00:41:33,960 --> 00:41:35,670
Yifei misses you a lot.

791
00:41:37,710 --> 00:41:39,230
I'm sure she wants to see you.

792
00:41:39,880 --> 00:41:41,760
Yifei might be overseas now,

793
00:41:42,190 --> 00:41:43,760
